Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:36.59,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.67,0:02:21.07,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,With the community still
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:23.87,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,shaken from last year's Slater's Quarry tragedy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.98,0:02:26.17,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,here in Boreham, it's fresh heartache.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.28,0:02:27.81,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,As the search for the missing women
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:30.08,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,moves into the end of its second day,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.18,0:02:32.90,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,hope is fading for Senator Kaplan's niece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:34.64,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Juno, and her five friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:38.32,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Just behind me I can see one of the cave rescue teams
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.62,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,emerging from the caverns.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:40.76,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,-Good luck, guys. -Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:42.50,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Chimney's pretty tight. You all be careful in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:43.50,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:45.89,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Sir, any signs of the missing women?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:49.09,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Do you think you'll find them alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:51.93,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,How does this compare to Slater's Quarry?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.36,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,That's enough now. Move back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:57.17,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Do you think you responded quickly enough this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:59.33,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,-Greg, leave it! -Greg!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:04.00,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,We're back on in four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.95,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,-Get some sleep. -You too, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:09.30,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Hey, you want to share a sleeping bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:11.15,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,What's that cologne you're wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:13.03,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Yeah, six hours of sweat and dirt
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.03,0:03:14.62,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,and all other kinds of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:16.46,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I think I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:18.43,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Lynch? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:22.53,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:25.47,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:32.13,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Look, get a tracker dog out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:34.54,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,See if you can find where she came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:37.18,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Yeah, all right, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:39.42,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Let's keep the lid on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:41.05,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,All right, I'm on my way to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:06.27,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Right, Doc, how is she? - She's resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:08.11,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,We had to sedate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:09.42,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I've got five girls missing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:10.44,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,and you put the one person
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:11.58,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,who knows where they are to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:13.37,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,She was hysterical.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:17.48,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Besides, she has no memory of the last two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:20.02,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Whatever happened to her, she's blanked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:22.42,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:24.29,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,It's only some minor cuts and bruises.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:27.06,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,But her clothes were completely stained in blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:29.63,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- So it's not her blood? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:31.95,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,But she's been in a fight, all right,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.73,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,because judging by her fingernails,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:36.77,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,she scratched some big chunks out of somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:38.75,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Test her clothes, get the blood type.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.94,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Get the blood type of the other five girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.65,0:04:46.78,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,All right, let's see what you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:55.88,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Hello, Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:04.27,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I'm Jenna Rios from Hyde County Sheriff's Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:07.90,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,This is Sheriff Vaines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:14.41,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- How you feeling? - Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:18.54,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You're safe. You're at Hyde County hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:22.58,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,We've been searching for you and your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:28.52,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Two days ago you all set off on a caving expedition
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:30.29,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,and you never came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:34.72,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,We've been following your Boreham Cavern flight plan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.76,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,but we found nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:40.76,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Can you tell us what happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:44.47,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:47.01,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I can't remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:57.08,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Sarah, your friends are still missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:00.92,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,We need you to help us find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:06.43,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Beth. - Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:09.20,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,What happened to Beth?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:13.59,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,What can you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:19.97,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,What about Juno?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:24.21,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Jessie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:28.81,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,-Where's Jessie? -Your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:36.02,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Sarah, Sarah,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:39.15,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I need you to listen to me carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:43.73,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Your daughter isn't here, Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:46.53,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,She died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:50.13,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- A year ago, in Scotland. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:54.04,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I know how hard this must be for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:58.98,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- but you have to try... - No, no. No! No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:01.45,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:47.06,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,This looks like the end of the trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:53.13,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- What's that? - That there's Chapel Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:01.78,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Cuffs, come here, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:04.68,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Go find them, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:17.25,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,One of these days I'm gonna come up here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:19.32,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,and help myself to some of this shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:26.59,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,What you found, boy? What you found?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:35.17,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Cuffs?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:49.86,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:03.27,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,-Sheriff. -Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:04.46,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Keep it under your hat,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:06.20,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,but we found one of the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:08.24,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Dog picked up her scent near the old Chapel Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:10.37,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- That's the other side of the county. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:14.81,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Don't tell me we've been looking in the wrong place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:17.11,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Listen, I don't want to shift the whole goddamn circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:18.58,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I just want a couple of volunteers to pick up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:21.25,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,where the dog left off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:22.59,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,All right, give us an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:29.32,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Cath, Greg, rise and shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:32.33,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Blood on Sarah Carter's clothes, A-positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:35.30,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Juno Kaplan is A-positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:38.17,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,So? I'm A-positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:39.60,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Half the state is A-positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:41.91,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Can she walk? - Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.60,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, you're not seriously gonna take her out...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:46.58,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Rios, get her dressed and get her in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:21.41,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,My granddaddy used to work down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:22.96,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,One time, him and two of his buddies
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:25.18,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,broke into a whole new cave system.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:26.54,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Really big.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:29.31,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Company bosses figured
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:31.68,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,there should be some rich pickings to be had,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.95,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,so they sent my granddaddy back down to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.19,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,have a good look-see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:37.22,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,He never come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.06,0:11:42.33,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Folks reckoned they must've broke clean through into hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:45.76,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,The devil was mighty pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:47.98,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,So you're telling me that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:50.00,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,there's an uncharted cave system down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:54.11,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.51,0:11:56.95,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,There's a map of the mines here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:11:59.59,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,If the caves are uncharted,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:01.41,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,we won't even know where to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:02.61,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Bring the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:07.38,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Come on, Dan, she's the only one been down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:10.13,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,All we gotta do is get a nod from her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:11.89,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,left or right. Narrows the search.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:14.46,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,There's a mountain full of caves and fuck-all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:16.43,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Could piggyback on the elevator cables.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:19.83,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You planning to go down there,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:21.60,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,why not go down there in style?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:23.92,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,What, this old shit still works?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:25.70,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Sonny, let me tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:28.02,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,this old shit-bucket will be working long time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:30.21,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,after that MP3 of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:32.00,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:34.84,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,All right, Ed, get it going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:41.35,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but Mommy's got to help people tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:45.02,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Chica, when Grandma tells you to go to bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:46.46,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,you go to bed, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:51.26,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Honey, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:55.27,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Okay, baby, I'll see you tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.91,0:13:00.09,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Rios, get yourself kitted and get her kitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:01.50,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,We're going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:13.18,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Okay, Sarah, I know this is difficult,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:15.64,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,but if you do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:17.99,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,it could help jog your memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:20.38,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Your friends could still be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:23.16,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You have to help us find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:36.75,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Hey, Sarah, this might fit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:41.19,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You want to lose that heavy metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:43.59,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Gun blast down there'd be like dynamite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:46.50,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Come on, I'll put them in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:48.68,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,My gun stays with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:54.66,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,This is a missing persons case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:57.26,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,What the hell do you think you're gonna find down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:21.19,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Mummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:23.19,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Right, let's get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:34.90,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:42.25,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You all ready to ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:43.71,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:44.57,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:58.58,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Hang on, just wait up a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.86,0:17:07.22,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Here, drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:13.42,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,She's okay. Let me worry about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:17.29,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Come on, Dan, let's get to the goddamn cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:23.84,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Listen. Down here, I call the shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.24,0:17:25.40,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Is that understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:28.17,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:30.71,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:17.63,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Should be a ladder down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:21.89,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,How long have I been teaching you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.73,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Your light is your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:35.44,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,All right. Okay, we've gotta go down another level.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:37.71,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Greg.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.46,0:18:51.52,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You gotta be fucking kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.02,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:20.86,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You know what's good?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:23.19,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Modern mines have metal props.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:26.61,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Miners prefer these old wooden ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.61,0:19:27.62,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:29.02,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,The metal ones don't give you any warning
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:31.13,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,when they're about to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:41.37,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,After yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:53.95,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Okay, we should hit the cave system somewhere up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:55.86,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Greg, go scout ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:57.29,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:05.60,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,And Cath, you're next. Deputy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:15.14,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I think I've found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:21.28,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.85,0:20:24.91,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,It's a pit pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:28.85,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Always a good sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:52.71,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,...Check it out. This is awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:16.56,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Greg, T.L.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:22.78,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Hey, hey. Don't... Don't touch anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:25.87,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,This place is thousands of years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:29.78,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Well, you're hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:30.52,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:35.82,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Sarah, do you recognize anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.65,0:21:58.41,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.09,0:22:40.52,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,It's okay. It's okay, she just got spooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:52.06,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Calcium deposits.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.94,0:22:56.18,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Let's keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:22:58.90,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,It's okay, come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.87,0:23:25.26,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Come on, Sheriff, you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.26,0:23:26.34,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I ain't that old yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.28,0:23:35.30,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Which way?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.38,0:23:39.87,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You recognize this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.25,0:23:45.38,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Cath, have a listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.94,0:24:39.51,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.51,0:24:42.64,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I don't know. I think I hear something.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.35,0:25:22.55,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.35,0:25:25.29,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Oh, my God! - Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.39,0:25:27.79,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Fuck! Sarah. Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.36,0:25:30.49,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,She's moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.49,0:25:33.66,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,No. There's no body heat. It's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.71,0:25:47.80,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Deputy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.41,0:25:51.18,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.95,0:25:59.48,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,She's been butchered.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.46,0:26:03.95,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Six girls came down to this cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.95,0:26:05.45,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,One came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.56,0:26:07.26,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Covered in her friends' blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.36,0:26:10.56,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Now, you tell me what the hell happened down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.67,0:26:11.47,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Wait... wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.47,0:26:12.76,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You think she had something to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.76,0:26:14.13,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- This is fucked up! - Dan, get your team out of my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.24,0:26:15.17,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Man, you brought her down... - Get off my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.27,0:26:16.60,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Greg! Save it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.31,0:26:21.04,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I thought she was a victim here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.05,0:26:23.27,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,What are you saying now, she's a suspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.38,0:26:25.28,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I think she knows something.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.38,0:26:27.87,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I still got missing girls down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.87,0:26:30.08,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,so let's keep our goddamn focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.19,0:26:31.68,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I should never have let you bring her down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.79,0:26:32.96,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I should never have let you...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.96,0:26:34.42,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Dan, I think she came through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.52,0:26:37.19,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,All right, Greg, take point. Take point!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.66,0:26:40.39,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,This is fucking bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.39,0:26:41.93,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Deputy, look after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.03,0:26:44.63,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,It's okay. Come on, you're gonna be...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.76,0:27:10.78,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Sarah, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.03,0:27:17.99,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I think there's something down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.99,0:27:19.97,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,We were attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.34,0:27:21.60,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,By what?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.94,0:27:23.00,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,There's nothing down here
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.00,0:27:24.91,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,that could have done this to a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.01,0:27:27.70,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Sarah, what can you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.61,0:27:31.71,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Sarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.25,0:27:35.24,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,We shouldn't stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.02,0:27:37.96,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You've got to try and think rationally.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.96,0:27:39.35,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You're scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.46,0:27:42.25,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Your mind's playing tricks on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.63,0:27:43.96,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I'm through.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.63,0:27:47.54,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,It's about a 50-foot crawl with some tight spots,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.54,0:27:48.56,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,and then it opens out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.67,0:27:50.38,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,All right, copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.38,0:27:52.10,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Sheriff, get your team together.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.20,0:27:53.57,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Greg, we're coming through.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.58,0:27:55.37,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Look out for them at the other end.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.14,0:28:00.08,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Okay, Rios, you go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.54,0:28:02.02,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I want you in front of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.02,0:28:04.54,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,She's not getting out of my sight from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.07,0:29:05.97,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Come on, you're almost there. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.34,0:29:09.00,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Hey! Whoa, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.38,0:29:10.94,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You need to breathe with me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.94,0:29:12.20,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You need to breathe, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.12,0:29:18.88,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Come on, keep it moving up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.33,0:29:26.52,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Get a move on, you're slowing down.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.00,0:29:36.97,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Why have you stopped? Get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.04,0:29:42.34,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,How are you feeling? All right? Hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.05,0:29:45.74,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Sarah... Sarah...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.88,0:29:47.91,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Rios!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.25,0:29:51.48,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Sarah!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.16,0:29:53.21,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Sarah!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.22,0:29:55.18,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,For Christ's sake, Rios.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.49,0:29:59.95,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Which way did she go? Which way?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.06,0:30:02.96,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.97,0:30:06.76,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,It's okay. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.38,0:30:23.22,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,That lady's a fucking psycho, Dan. Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.62,0:30:25.85,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- You okay? - I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.96,0:30:27.74,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Look at me. How's it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.74,0:30:29.08,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You want to kiss it better?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.19,0:30:31.46,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- He's fine. - Where's Vaines?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.56,0:30:34.25,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,He took off after Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.25,0:30:36.69,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Fuck! He doesn't even have a radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.13,0:30:38.47,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Five minutes in these honeycombs,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.48,0:30:39.74,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,they'll both be lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.74,0:30:41.64,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Okay, listen to me, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.74,0:30:42.88,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,We've gotta catch up on them
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.88,0:30:43.67,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,before they get too far ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.77,0:30:45.51,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,This time, we stick together.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.51,0:30:47.40,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You understand? Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.44,0:30:49.71,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Yeah, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.48,0:31:29.45,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.92,0:31:33.01,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Okay, there's falling rock here,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.12,0:31:34.72,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,which, as you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.72,0:31:36.32,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,means the roof's unstable,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.03,0:31:38.89,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,so we have to tread carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.93,0:31:43.00,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Rios? You stick with me, okay? Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.84,0:34:36.33,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Cath, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.34,0:34:38.00,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Take it easy, that's gotta last.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.94,0:34:43.28,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Cath, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.41,0:34:45.90,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Cath, speak to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.43,0:34:58.89,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Dan, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.89,0:35:01.12,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I'm here, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.53,0:35:03.29,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.40,0:35:04.97,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I'm stuck in a boulder choke.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.97,0:35:07.23,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,And I need something to support the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.34,0:35:10.00,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,All right, all right. Don't you panic, don't you panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.11,0:35:13.13,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Listen to me. I'm gonna get you. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.48,0:35:15.92,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,We'll work at this end, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.93,0:35:16.84,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.41,0:35:19.90,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You sit tight, we'll get to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.98,0:35:22.04,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.36,0:35:29.09,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Jesus. Come here, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.96,0:35:33.55,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Come on, come on, come on. Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.43,0:35:35.42,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.73,0:35:39.67,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Come on. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.07,0:35:45.60,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Fuck! Fucking trigger-happy Americans. - Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.94,0:35:48.07,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Fucking only answer they've got to anything is a fucking gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.18,0:35:49.67,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Dan, don't let her hear you this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.78,0:35:51.54,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,There's a fucking ton of rubble between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.54,0:35:53.22,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,She couldn't hear a fucking rock concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.32,0:35:54.44,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.66,0:36:04.75,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.40,0:36:17.27,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Okay. Okay, Cath.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.17,0:36:19.11,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.41,0:36:24.42,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,We can't get through to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.42,0:36:26.91,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Well, can't you drill it or det it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.09,0:36:31.35,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You know we can't. It's too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.72,0:36:34.62,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You're gonna have to work yourself free
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.72,0:36:36.93,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I can't, Dan, it'll crush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.93,0:36:37.63,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I need you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.33,0:36:46.93,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Okay,I'm gonna find another way around to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.14,0:36:52.23,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Okay. - I'll get to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.84,0:36:56.84,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I'm scared, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.78,0:37:01.90,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,That's good, yeah? Fear keeps you alert,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.90,0:37:04.69,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,it keeps you alive, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.45,0:37:10.12,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I promise you,I won't stop till I get to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.23,0:37:11.52,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.53,0:37:15.37,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Maybe I should stay with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.37,0:37:17.97,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You know we can't help her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.81,0:37:25.97,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You hang in there, teammate.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.58,0:37:29.70,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- No worries. - Okay, Cath.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.58,0:37:33.41,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Are you dry?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.48,0:37:37.94,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Yeah. - So you'll keep warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.05,0:37:39.77,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You keep drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.78,0:37:42.79,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You stick with the drill, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.89,0:37:44.29,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.03,0:37:47.67,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,We're gonna have to move off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.67,0:37:50.47,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,So you'll probably lose the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.87,0:37:52.70,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You stay positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.37,0:37:57.03,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Okay. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.18,0:38:04.41,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,We're walking away. You stay on channel one.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.51,0:38:07.74,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll be on channel one.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.82,0:38:11.48,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You got your chance now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.35,0:39:48.34,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.32,0:39:52.29,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.71,0:40:12.11,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.73,0:40:37.89,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Are these animal bones? - Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.99,0:40:57.68,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Dan! Dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.77,0:41:19.54,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Here we are, morning after the night before.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.64,0:41:21.80,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Here we go. Look at this face.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.91,0:41:23.14,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Wake up, ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.25,0:41:24.74,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I feel like a pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.85,0:41:27.58,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Now there's some water. - It's not nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.68,0:41:30.24,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- We all ready for this big, exciting day? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.35,0:41:32.08,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,That's Juno.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.62,0:41:37.62,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I'll believe that when I see it, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.49,0:41:39.83,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.93,0:41:42.36,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Yeah, I feel good. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.30,0:41:47.73,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Recording for... - For National Geographic.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.84,0:41:49.24,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,For National Geographic.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.34,0:41:51.17,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Once again... - Recording our trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.27,0:41:52.77,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,To Boreham boredom Cavern.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.77,0:41:54.77,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,How do you think Sarah's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.88,0:41:56.65,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Do you think she's ready for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.65,0:41:58.68,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I mean, she just seemed a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.78,0:42:00.77,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You cut the camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.19,0:42:09.78,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Sarah? - Put it away for, like, two minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.39,0:42:14.16,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Where is that? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.26,0:42:15.47,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Holly! Could you take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.48,0:42:16.96,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I just want to take a few more shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.07,0:42:19.00,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,This cave's a lot cooler than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.10,0:42:21.97,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- This wasn't in the book. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.07,0:42:26.17,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Maybe that last jelly custard wasn't a really good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.28,0:42:30.37,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- How much further, do you think? - Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.48,0:42:32.47,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- You sure? - Yeah, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.18,0:42:34.34,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Okay, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.12,0:42:41.95,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Do you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.13,0:42:47.53,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.20,0:42:53.26,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Dead animals, hundreds of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.37,0:42:55.23,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,-That's here. -This is not good, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.34,0:42:58.74,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,-Can we get out of here? Which way? -That's this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.84,0:43:02.83,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,-Come on. I don't know. -What do you mean you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.95,0:43:04.42,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,There's no breeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.42,0:43:06.81,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,It could be any one of these tunnels! Take your pick!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.92,0:43:08.18,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Fuck it!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.28,0:43:10.18,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,-Hello! -Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.29,0:43:13.52,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Is there anybody there?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.62,0:43:16.18,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.29,0:43:19.16,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,What the fuck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.20,0:43:26.93,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Greg! Greg!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.48,0:43:36.27,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Greg! Greg, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.29,0:44:20.62,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.72,0:44:22.75,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Rios, you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.86,0:44:26.59,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Dan, I'm here! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.43,0:44:31.92,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Dan! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.07,0:44:38.04,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.39,0:44:59.36,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Rios!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.23,0:45:03.22,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Rios!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.44,0:45:11.53,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Rios! Where are you? Let me know where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.94,0:45:13.27,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.04,0:45:17.17,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.77,0:46:11.56,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You let him die.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.28,0:46:26.54,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,What the fuck was that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.95,0:46:30.75,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It's just your mind playing tricks on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.15,0:47:39.95,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Dan? Greg?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.09,0:47:46.75,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Dan, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.36,0:47:51.23,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Can you hear me, Dan?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.02,0:49:49.61,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.29,0:49:52.31,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.82,0:49:55.88,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I didn't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.99,0:49:59.43,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,They're blind. They track sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.43,0:50:00.72,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You're louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.59,0:51:08.19,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Greg! Greg! - Cath!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.60,0:51:17.33,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Where's everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.37,0:51:19.67,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,We got split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.38,0:51:23.57,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- What the fuck are these things? - I don't know. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.68,0:51:29.67,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- I want my fucking torch. - Shit. Sorry. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.79,0:51:33.38,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Is this okay? Okay? Okay. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.96,0:51:41.09,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Run. Run! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.77,0:52:26.24,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.34,0:52:28.21,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.65,0:52:34.95,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.76,0:52:49.59,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Fuck. Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.18,0:53:38.30,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.75,0:53:39.94,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.18,0:53:41.27,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Can you hear me? Is there anybody out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.38,0:53:42.64,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Come in! Anybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.75,0:53:44.88,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Up! Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.85,0:53:47.05,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.03,0:53:56.19,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Dan's dead. - Turn it off. Turn it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.30,0:53:58.09,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Come in. Anybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.17,0:54:06.27,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Are you there? Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.14,0:54:12.27,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Come on, can you pick this up? Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.62,0:54:19.35,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Dan? Dan, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.82,0:54:21.98,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Dan, it's Cath. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.52,0:54:25.65,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Dan's dead. - Dan. Come in, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.00,0:54:28.45,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Vaines had his radio, Cath.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.45,0:54:30.69,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,We don't know that. We... He wasn't clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.80,0:54:33.29,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Dan? Dan, come in. Dan?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.30,0:54:36.29,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Give me that. Give me. Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.40,0:54:38.96,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I left him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.07,0:54:41.63,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Those... Those fucking things attacked us and I left him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.74,0:54:44.21,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,No. No, he promised he'd come back. He promised he'd come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.31,0:54:47.34,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I heard him scream, Cath.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.05,0:54:49.41,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I heard him scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.05,0:54:54.15,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,He's gone, Cath, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.72,0:54:59.39,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.17,0:55:06.19,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I ain't gonna run out on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.54,0:55:12.51,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You even try, and I'll kill you myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.94,0:55:18.94,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,We gotta move. Stay quiet. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.43,0:55:34.52,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.43,0:55:41.66,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Fuck. - Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.77,0:55:43.26,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.94,0:55:46.70,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- You'll have to jump. - It's too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.94,0:55:51.91,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Use her to get across.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.85,0:55:58.15,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.65,0:56:00.14,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Fuck! - We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.26,0:56:02.19,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Fuck! Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.29,0:56:03.48,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.70,0:56:11.16,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,All right, push forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.83,0:57:46.02,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Greg!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.39,0:57:48.12,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Greg!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.17,0:57:54.83,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Greg!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.88,0:58:41.21,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Got washed out by the water last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.85,0:58:46.41,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I... I can't go down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.82,0:58:50.26,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,The water's flowing. There's a way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.73,0:58:58.32,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,No, no. Wait. Wait, please. Wait. Please. Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.73,1:00:41.90,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Sarah. Sarah. Sarah! Sarah!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.00,1:00:43.53,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,God.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.91,1:00:48.24,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,No, no, no. Sarah!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.68,1:00:57.38,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Come. Come. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.20,1:01:13.39,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- It stops here? - It's a dead-end.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.50,1:01:15.30,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,There's no way through?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.40,1:01:18.96,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- No. - Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.71,1:01:22.54,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Fucking water.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.23,1:02:14.29,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Hi, baby girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.96,1:02:18.56,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Hiya. It's Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.80,1:02:25.83,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I... I just wanted to let you know...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.24,1:02:29.14,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,That I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.58,1:02:34.51,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I want you to be good.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.35,1:02:37.61,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,And kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.25,1:02:40.55,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,And caring.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.42,1:02:45.29,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I want you to be a good person.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.50,1:02:50.83,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You're so special, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.40,1:03:03.31,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Te quiero, te extra, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.48,1:03:08.04,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,My daughter's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.52,1:03:10.64,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.26,1:03:18.05,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Everything you just said,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.05,1:03:21.19,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,you tell it to her face. We're not dead yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.23,1:03:24.03,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Come on. We'll keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.62,1:04:54.92,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Juno!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.19,1:05:02.15,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Juno, I'm here to help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.26,1:05:06.13,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Get you out. You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.50,1:05:08.73,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I'm here with Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.52,1:09:58.62,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,God.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.19,1:10:01.99,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,What the fuck is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.53,1:10:05.02,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.76,1:10:35.09,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Now I wish I was back in the water.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.16,1:12:14.22,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,What are these things?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.93,1:12:17.36,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Death.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.52,1:12:39.11,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Your friends, they're all dead?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.22,1:12:40.69,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.03,1:12:48.39,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,How the fuck did you find this hellhole?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.50,1:12:52.49,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Juno brought us here. She wanted us all to discover it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.17,1:12:57.47,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,She said she wanted to name it after me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.91,1:13:00.53,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Why? - Guilt.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.78,1:13:04.97,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,What happened between the two of you?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.15,1:13:07.61,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,My husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.55,1:13:10.81,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,She had an affair with my husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.95,1:13:13.78,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,What happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.36,1:13:22.09,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,It was just Juno and me left.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.66,1:13:25.57,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Those things were coming for us,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.57,1:13:28.66,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,so I hurt her so I could get away.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.47,1:13:33.70,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,She left my friend Beth dying.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.68,1:13:36.07,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.51,1:13:42.78,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,When I found Beth, I had to put her out of her misery.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.92,1:13:50.41,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Save your torch.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.08,1:14:49.01,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,No, Juno, wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.45,1:14:51.92,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,We came to get you out! Juno.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.02,1:14:55.98,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Sarah brought us back down here. She brought us back.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.09,1:14:59.49,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Juno. Sarah is your friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.41,1:15:15.74,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- So you're the rescue party? - We're what's left.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.58,1:15:20.51,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Come on. We gotta get out of here. - Okay, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.61,1:15:23.45,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Listen. Those things hunt above ground.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.55,1:15:25.45,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I think I know which way they go.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.45,1:15:27.65,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,They must have a route to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.75,1:15:28.91,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,So, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.02,1:15:33.58,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, so what? We go to where they feed?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.69,1:15:34.68,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Are you fucking kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.80,1:15:38.99,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Do you want to live? Silence is your best weapon.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.10,1:15:41.40,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Follow me. - We're following the water.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.50,1:15:44.13,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I ain't going in no goddamn water. Juno knows the way out.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.24,1:15:46.30,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,So how come you're still here?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.41,1:15:49.84,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Because my light died, I had no equipment,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.94,1:15:51.48,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,and my climbing partner put
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.48,1:15:53.88,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,a pick through my leg and ran out on me...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.98,1:15:56.47,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,There isn't time for this, God damn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.58,1:15:59.05,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,We want to get out of here alive, we follow Juno.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.15,1:16:00.98,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,No fucking way.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.09,1:16:02.18,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,God damn it! I brought
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.18,1:16:04.32,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,you into this hellhole, I'm taking you out.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.53,1:16:08.69,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Wait! - What? It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.80,1:16:10.42,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Chief! - Shut up, Rios.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.67,1:16:14.90,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Let's move.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.38,1:17:03.04,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,We'll have to go single file.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.43,1:17:23.56,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Spread your weight.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.58,1:17:39.55,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Keep it steady.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.23,1:17:50.49,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Easy, easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.77,1:17:53.93,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,We really should do this one at a time.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.03,1:17:57.27,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,You ran out on her, but you ain't running out on me,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.37,1:17:59.27,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,so let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.80,1:18:27.06,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.19,1:18:48.55,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Help me! - Give me the bag.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.19,1:18:54.89,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Juno, help me, please! Juno!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.71,1:19:08.70,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,My arm! Pull me up!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.21,1:19:14.65,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Grab my pick.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.48,1:19:19.18,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Okay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.29,1:19:21.12,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Cut. - What? Cut what?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.22,1:19:23.16,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Cut it, or they'll both die!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.26,1:19:25.45,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Just fucking cut it!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.80,1:19:33.16,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- Do it now! - Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.98,1:19:52.21,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.87,1:20:07.46,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.75,1:20:24.61,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Fuck. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.39,1:20:26.72,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,We gotta move.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.80,1:20:37.35,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,We gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.17,1:20:42.76,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Rios.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.07,1:20:47.56,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.54,1:20:50.98,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.95,1:24:14.00,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Come on. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.27,1:25:20.61,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- I can't... - No.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.62,1:25:30.92,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.02,1:25:33.55,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,- I'm sorry. - It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.66,1:25:35.59,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.41,1:25:50.84,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.28,1:25:56.48,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Sarah, we can't stay here.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.99,1:26:05.19,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Sarah. We have to get out of here now.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.74,1:26:18.23,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.34,1:26:20.10,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.92,1:28:45.94,英语,说话人,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:52.09,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,阿巴拉契亚山脉 美国
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:36.59,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:39.09,简中,说话人,0,0,0,, 抢修服务车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.09,0:02:13.09,简中,说话人,0,0,0,, 黑暗侵袭 2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.67,0:02:21.07,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,公众还未摆脱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:23.87,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,斯莱特采石场悲剧的阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.98,0:02:26.17,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,在博勒姆这里 又发生了新的惨剧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.28,0:02:27.81,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,由于搜索失踪女孩的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:30.08,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,已进入了第二天的尾声
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.18,0:02:32.90,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,卡普兰参议员的侄女朱诺 和她的五个伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:34.64,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,生还的希望越发渺茫了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:38.32,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,就在我身后 能看到其中一支洞穴救援队
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.62,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,刚从洞里出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:40.76,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 好运 伙计们 - 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:42.50,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,洞口很紧 你们都要小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:43.50,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我们会注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:45.89,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,先生 是否发现失踪女孩的踪迹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:49.09,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你认为她们还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:51.93,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,这次的情况比起斯莱特采石场事件如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.36,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,够了 退后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:57.17,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你觉得这次反应时间够快吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:59.33,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 格雷格 别理她 - 格雷格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:04.00,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我们四小时内回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.95,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 去睡一会儿 - 你也一样 老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:09.30,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,能跟你合用一个睡袋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:11.15,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你用的什么古龙水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:13.03,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,哦对 进洞六小时 浑身汗臭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.03,0:03:14.62,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,泥泞不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:16.46,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我还是别猜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:18.43,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,林奇 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:22.53,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:25.47,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:32.13,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,听着 带条追踪犬过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:34.54,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,找到她出来的洞口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:37.18,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,好的 还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:39.42,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,这事先别声张
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:41.05,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,好的 我马上去医院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:06.27,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 医生 她怎么样了 - 她在休息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:08.11,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我们得让她镇静
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:09.42,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,还有五个女孩没找到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:10.44,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你却让唯一一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:11.58,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,知道线索的人睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:13.37,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,她有点不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:17.48,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,另外 这两天的事她都不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:20.02,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,不管那时发生了什么 她都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:22.42,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,伤势怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:24.29,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,只是些轻微的割伤和挫伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:27.06,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,但她的衣服却沾满了血迹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:29.63,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 不是她的血吗 - 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:31.95,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,但她打斗过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.73,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,从她的指甲判断
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:36.77,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,她曾狠狠地抓挠过某人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:38.75,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,化验她衣服上血迹的血型
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.94,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,和其他五个女孩做一下对比
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.65,0:04:46.78,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,好吧 看看你能发现点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:55.88,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你好 莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:04.27,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我是海德县警局的珍娜·里奥斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:07.90,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,这位是万尼斯警长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:14.41,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 你感觉怎么样 - 我在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:18.54,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你现在很安全 这里是海德县医院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:22.58,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我们一直在寻找你和你的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:28.52,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,两天前 你们去洞穴探险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:30.29,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,但一直没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:34.72,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我们根据你们的博勒姆洞穴探险计划搜寻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.76,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,但什么也没找到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:40.76,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,能告诉我们 你们遇到了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:44.47,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:47.01,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,什么都记不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:57.08,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,莎拉 你的同伴们还没找到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:00.92,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我们需要你的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:06.43,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 贝丝 - 贝丝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:09.20,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,贝丝怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:13.59,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你能想起些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:19.97,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,记得朱诺吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:24.21,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,杰西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:28.81,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 杰西在哪里 - 你女儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:36.02,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,莎拉 莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:39.15,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我要你认真听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:43.73,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你女儿不在这里 莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:46.53,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,她已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:50.13,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 一年前 在苏格兰 - 不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:54.04,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我知道这对你来说有多难接受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:58.98,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 但你必须尝试… - 不 那不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:01.45,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:47.06,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,看起来痕迹到这里就没了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:53.13,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 那是什么 - 那是小教堂煤矿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:01.78,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,卡夫斯 过来 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:04.68,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,去找到他们 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:17.25,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,过几天我会过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:19.32,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,处理一下这些垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:26.59,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,找到什么了 小子 你找到什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:35.17,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,卡夫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:49.86,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:03.27,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 警长 - 丹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:04.46,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,别声张
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:06.20,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我们找到了其中一个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:08.24,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,警犬追踪她的气味到了老教堂煤矿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:10.37,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 那在县城的另一边 - 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:14.81,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,别告诉我 我们一直在瞎忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:17.11,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,听着 你不用把整个团队都带来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:18.58,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我只想要几个志愿者去搜索一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:21.25,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,警犬进去后就跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:22.59,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,好吧 一小时后见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:29.32,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,凯丝 格雷格该起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:32.33,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,莎拉·卡特衣服上的血迹 是A型阳性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:35.30,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,朱诺·卡普兰也是A型阳性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:38.17,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,那又怎样 我也是这个血型
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:39.60,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,半个州的人都是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:41.91,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 她能走吗 - 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.60,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,等等 你们不会真要带她去…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:46.58,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,里奥斯 让她穿上衣服 带她上车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:21.41,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我爷爷以前在那下面工作过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:22.96,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,有一次 他和他的两个伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:25.18,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,闯入了一个未知的洞穴系统
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:26.54,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,非常大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:29.31,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,公司老板们以为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:31.68,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,那里资源应该很丰富
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.95,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,于是他们派我祖父
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.19,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,下去探查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:37.22,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,他再也没回来过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.06,0:11:42.33,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,人们猜想他们是闯入了地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:45.76,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,惹怒了魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:47.98,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你是告诉我说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:50.00,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,那下面有个未知的洞穴系统吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:54.11,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,太酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.51,0:11:56.95,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,这有张矿井地图
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:11:59.59,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,如果那洞穴没被探查过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:01.41,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我们可能连入口都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:02.61,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,把那女孩带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:07.38,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,行了 丹 只有她去过那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:10.13,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我们只需要她点点头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:11.89,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,左边或右边 指示搜索的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:14.46,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,那山遍布着未知洞穴 我们没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:16.43,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,那可以顺着那电梯电缆滑下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:19.83,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,如果你们要下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:21.60,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,干嘛不直接坐电梯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:23.92,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,啥意思 这老东西还能用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:25.70,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,小家伙 告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:28.02,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,这老东西肯定会比
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:30.21,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你的MP3的寿命长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:32.00,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,随你怎么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:34.84,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,好吧 爱德 准备下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:41.35,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 但妈妈今晚要帮助别人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:45.02,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,宝贝 奶奶叫你睡觉的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:46.46,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你要听话 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:51.26,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,宝贝 我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:55.27,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,好的 宝贝 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.91,0:13:00.09,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,里奥斯 你们两个装备好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:01.50,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我们要下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:13.18,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,好吧 莎拉 我知道这很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:15.64,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,但如果你下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:17.99,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,也许会有助于你恢复记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:20.38,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你的同伴们可能还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:23.16,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你得帮我们找到他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:36.75,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,莎拉 这件可能合适你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:41.19,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你们别带枪下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:43.59,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,在下面开枪就像是爆破
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:46.50,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,拿来吧 我一起放车里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:48.68,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我在枪在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:54.66,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我们只是去找失踪的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:57.26,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你觉得下面能有什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:21.19,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:23.19,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,好吧 我们开始行动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:34.90,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:42.25,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你们准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:43.71,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,没问题 开动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:44.57,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:58.58,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,慢点 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.86,0:17:07.22,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,来 喝口水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:13.42,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,她没事 不用你操心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:17.29,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,来吧 丹 我们进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:23.84,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,听着 在下面 我说了算
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.24,0:17:25.40,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:28.17,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:30.71,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:17.63,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,那里应该有个梯子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:21.89,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我教你多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.73,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你的灯光就是你的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:35.44,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,好吧 我们再下一层
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:37.71,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,格雷格
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.46,0:18:51.52,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.02,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:20.86,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,想听听好消息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:23.19,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,现代矿井都是金属架构
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:26.61,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,而矿工则喜欢老式的木质坑道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.61,0:19:27.62,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:29.02,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,金属架构矿井快垮塌的之时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:31.13,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,不会给你任何警示
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:41.37,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你先走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:53.95,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,那上面应该就是洞穴系统
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:55.86,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,格雷格 先上去探查
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:57.29,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:05.60,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,凯丝 你下一个 副警长过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:15.14,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我想我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:21.28,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,那是啥玩意儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.85,0:20:24.91,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,是匹井下小马[旧时井下运输工具]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:28.85,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,总有好兆头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.56,0:20:29.05,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,危险 请勿入内
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:52.71,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,…看啊 太不可思议了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:16.56,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,格雷格 热释光摄像机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:22.78,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,别…别碰任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:25.87,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,这地方有几千年历史
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:29.78,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你身材真好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:30.52,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,拿开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:35.82,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,莎拉 你能想起什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.65,0:21:58.41,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.09,0:22:40.52,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,没事 没事 她只是被吓着了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:52.06,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,钙质沉积
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.94,0:22:56.18,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我们继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:22:58.90,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,没事的 来吧 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.87,0:23:25.26,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,来吧 警长 你能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.26,0:23:26.34,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我还没那么老
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.28,0:23:35.30,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,走哪条路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.38,0:23:39.87,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你能认出这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.25,0:23:45.38,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,凯丝 测听一下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.94,0:24:39.51,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,听到什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.51,0:24:42.64,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我也不知道 好像有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.35,0:25:22.55,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.35,0:25:25.29,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 上帝啊 - 见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.39,0:25:27.79,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,妈的 莎拉 看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.36,0:25:30.49,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,她在动
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.49,0:25:33.66,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,不 没体温了 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.71,0:25:47.80,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,副警长
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.41,0:25:51.18,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.95,0:25:59.48,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,她是被屠杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.46,0:26:03.95,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,六个女孩到这洞里
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.95,0:26:05.45,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,只有一个出去
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.56,0:26:07.26,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,浑身都是她同伴的血迹
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.36,0:26:10.56,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,告诉我 这里到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.67,0:26:11.47,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.47,0:26:12.76,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你认为是她干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.76,0:26:14.13,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 这可真操蛋 - 丹 叫你的队员让开
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.24,0:26:15.17,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 伙计 你带她下来… - 少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.27,0:26:16.60,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,格雷格 别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.31,0:26:21.04,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,她不是这里的遇难者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.05,0:26:23.27,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你现在是说 她是个嫌疑犯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.38,0:26:25.28,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我觉得她了解内情
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.38,0:26:27.87,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,这里还有几个女孩下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.87,0:26:30.08,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我们得集中注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.19,0:26:31.68,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我真不该让你带她下来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.79,0:26:32.96,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我真不该…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.96,0:26:34.42,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,丹 我想她是从这里出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.52,0:26:37.19,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,好吧 格雷格 你带路 带路
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.66,0:26:40.39,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,这真他妈的太荒谬了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.39,0:26:41.93,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,副警长 看好她
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.03,0:26:44.63,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,没事了 走吧 你会…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.76,0:27:10.78,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,莎拉 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.03,0:27:17.99,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,这下面有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.99,0:27:19.97,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我们被攻击了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.34,0:27:21.60,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,被什么攻击了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.94,0:27:23.00,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,这下面没什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.00,0:27:24.91,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,能把一个人弄成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.01,0:27:27.70,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,莎拉 你还记得什么
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.61,0:27:31.71,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.25,0:27:35.24,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我们不该留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.02,0:27:37.96,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你要尽量理性思考
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.96,0:27:39.35,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你被吓坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.46,0:27:42.25,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,所以产生了幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.63,0:27:43.96,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.63,0:27:47.54,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,大概要爬五十英尺 有些地方有点窄
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.54,0:27:48.56,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,爬出来就宽敞了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.67,0:27:50.38,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,好吧 收到
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.38,0:27:52.10,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,警长 集合队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.20,0:27:53.57,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,格雷格 我们现在就过来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.58,0:27:55.37,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,在出口接应他们
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.14,0:28:00.08,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,里奥斯 你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.54,0:28:02.02,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我要你在她前面
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.02,0:28:04.54,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,现在开始 她不能离开我的视线范围
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.07,0:29:05.97,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,过来 就快到了 再过来点
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.34,0:29:09.00,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.38,0:29:10.94,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,和我一起做深呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.94,0:29:12.20,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你得深呼吸 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.12,0:29:18.88,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,快爬 继续爬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.33,0:29:26.52,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,快啊 你太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.00,0:29:36.97,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你怎么停了 快爬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.04,0:29:42.34,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你还好吗 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.05,0:29:45.74,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,莎拉…莎拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.88,0:29:47.91,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,里奥斯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.25,0:29:51.48,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.16,0:29:53.21,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.22,0:29:55.18,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,不是吧 里奥斯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.49,0:29:59.95,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,她走的哪条路 哪条路
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.06,0:30:02.96,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.97,0:30:06.76,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,没事了 没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.38,0:30:23.22,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,丹 那女人就是他妈个神经病 上帝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.62,0:30:25.85,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 你还好吗 - 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.96,0:30:27.74,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,看着我 感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.74,0:30:29.08,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你吻一下更好
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.19,0:30:31.46,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 他没事 - 万尼斯去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.56,0:30:34.25,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,他去追莎拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.25,0:30:36.69,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,妈的 他没带对讲机
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.13,0:30:38.47,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,这些洞穴进去五分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.48,0:30:39.74,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,他们都会迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.74,0:30:41.64,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,大家听着 都听着
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.74,0:30:42.88,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,趁他们还没走远
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.88,0:30:43.67,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我们得赶上他们
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.77,0:30:45.51,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,这次 我们一起行动
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.51,0:30:47.40,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,明白吗 好吧 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.44,0:30:49.71,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.48,0:31:29.45,简中,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.92,0:31:33.01,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,这里有落石
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.12,0:31:34.72,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,如你们所知
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.72,0:31:36.32,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,这说明洞顶不稳固
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.03,0:31:38.89,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我们过去时得千万小心
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.93,0:31:43.00,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,里奥斯 你跟紧我 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.84,0:34:36.33,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,凯丝 能听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.34,0:34:38.00,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,别紧张 塌方结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.94,0:34:43.28,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,凯丝 听到请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.41,0:34:45.90,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,凯丝 说话
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.43,0:34:58.89,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,丹 你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.89,0:35:01.12,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我在 我在
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.53,0:35:03.29,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.40,0:35:04.97,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我被卡在石缝里了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.97,0:35:07.23,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我需要有东西顶住这些石头
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.34,0:35:10.00,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,知道了 知道了 别慌 别慌
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.11,0:35:13.13,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,听着 我会救你出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.48,0:35:15.92,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我们会从洞口挖过来 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.93,0:35:16.84,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,听着
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.41,0:35:19.90,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你别动 我们会救你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.98,0:35:22.04,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.36,0:35:29.09,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,天哪 过来 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.96,0:35:33.55,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,快啊 快啊 老天
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.43,0:35:35.42,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,丹
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.73,0:35:39.67,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,快啊 快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.07,0:35:45.60,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 操 去你妈的乱开枪的美国佬 - 丹
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.94,0:35:48.07,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,就他妈知道乱开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.18,0:35:49.67,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,丹 别让她听见你这状态
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.78,0:35:51.54,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,这儿他妈有一堆石头阻隔着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.54,0:35:53.22,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,这边就算开他妈演唱会她都不会察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.32,0:35:54.44,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,丹
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.66,0:36:04.75,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.40,0:36:17.27,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,好吧 好吧 凯丝
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.17,0:36:19.11,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.41,0:36:24.42,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我们挖不通这石堆
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.42,0:36:26.91,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,就不能钻开它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.09,0:36:31.35,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你知道不行的 太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.72,0:36:34.62,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你得自己想办法出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.72,0:36:36.93,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我没办法 丹 我乱动就会被压死
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.93,0:36:37.63,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我需要你帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.33,0:36:46.93,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,好吧 我去找找别的路
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.14,0:36:52.23,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 好 - 我会找到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.84,0:36:56.84,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,丹 我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.78,0:37:01.90,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,这很好 不是吗 恐惧会让你提高警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.90,0:37:04.69,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,警惕能让你生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.45,0:37:10.12,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我保证 找不到你我决不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.23,0:37:11.52,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.53,0:37:15.37,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,也许我该留下来陪她
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.37,0:37:17.97,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你知道待在这也无济于事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.81,0:37:25.97,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,坚持住 伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.58,0:37:29.70,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 别担心 - 好的 凯丝
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.58,0:37:33.41,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,衣服没湿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.48,0:37:37.94,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 没有 - 那你能保持身体暖和了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.05,0:37:39.77,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,随时补充水分
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.78,0:37:42.79,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,严格按照训练内容来做 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.89,0:37:44.29,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.03,0:37:47.67,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我们现在得出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.67,0:37:50.47,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,信号可能会暂时中断
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.87,0:37:52.70,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,别沮丧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.37,0:37:57.03,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 好的 - 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.18,0:38:04.41,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我们动身了 你保持在一频道
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.51,0:38:07.74,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,好的 我会在一频道
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.82,0:38:11.48,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你专心找路 把握好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.35,0:39:48.34,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.32,0:39:52.29,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.71,0:40:12.11,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,这他妈是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.73,0:40:37.89,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 这些都是骨头吗 - 天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.99,0:40:57.68,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,丹 丹
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.77,0:41:19.54,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,开始录啦 宿醉的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.64,0:41:21.80,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,瞧瞧这张脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.91,0:41:23.14,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,醒醒吧 女士们
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.25,0:41:24.74,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我肯定像个猪头似的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.85,0:41:27.58,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 这个看上去好多了 - 得了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.68,0:41:30.24,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 都准备好迎接这令人兴奋的一天了吧 - 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.35,0:41:32.08,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,这是朱诺
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.62,0:41:37.62,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我亲眼见到才会相信 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.49,0:41:39.83,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.93,0:41:42.36,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 感觉挺好 - 好
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.30,0:41:47.73,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 此录像是为 - 是为国家地理录制的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.84,0:41:49.24,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,为国家地理录制的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.34,0:41:51.17,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 重来一次 - 此录像是为
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.27,0:41:52.77,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我们到博雷汉姆荒废矿坑探险而录制
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.77,0:41:54.77,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你觉得莎拉状态怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.88,0:41:56.65,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你觉得她准备好参加这次探险了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.65,0:41:58.68,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我觉得她好像有些
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.78,0:42:00.77,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你关相机了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.19,0:42:09.78,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 莎拉 - 把那玩意儿拿开 几分钟也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.39,0:42:14.16,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 她们是在哪里 - 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.26,0:42:15.47,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,天哪 别拍了行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.48,0:42:16.96,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,我只是想多记录下一点内容
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.07,0:42:19.00,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,这矿坑比我想象中的阴冷多了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.10,0:42:21.97,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 在书里可学不到这些 - 这下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.07,0:42:26.17,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,早知道刚才就不吃那果冻布丁了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.28,0:42:30.37,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 你觉得还有多深 - 谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.48,0:42:32.47,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 当真 - 是的 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.18,0:42:34.34,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,伙计们 都还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.12,0:42:41.95,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,你们听到什么声音了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.13,0:42:47.53,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,就这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.20,0:42:53.26,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,动物的尸骨 成百上千的尸骨
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.37,0:42:55.23,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 是我们现在待的地方 - 伙计们 不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.34,0:42:58.74,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 咱们出去好吗 路在哪边 - 就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.84,0:43:02.83,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 快啊 我不知道 - 什么叫不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.95,0:43:04.42,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,察觉不到风向
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.42,0:43:06.81,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,每个路口都可能是出路 做决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.92,0:43:08.18,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.28,0:43:10.18,简中,说话人,0,0,0,,- 有人吗 - 别喊了
